
### Admin login
POST http://localhost:4000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@mail.com",
  "password": "admin"
}

### Read all USERS & AUTHORS (email)
GET http://localhost:4000/admin/users

### Block User
PUT http://localhost:4000/admin/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isActive": false
}


### Activate User
PUT http://localhost:4000/admin/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isActive": true
}